Readers of the most popular UK newspaper website, The Guardian, voted Half-Life 2 Game of the Year 2004. Readers logged on to vote in The Guardian's Annual Readers' Poll and Half-Life 2 garnered more votes than any game in all the categories. <br/><br/>Visit The Guardian's main site <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/online/story/0,3605,1369063,00.html">here</a>. For the full results the poll is also listed on their dedicated <a href="http://blogs.guardian.co.uk/games/archives/cat_games_of_the_year_2004.html">Gamesblog</a>.<br/></p>
